<td id="F9266ADD541E65D25FCAECB0790DD533" colspan="1" pageId="14" pageNumber="37" rowspan="1">Lemmas unawned, 11-20 mm long; glumes tapering from midlength or above, flat or rounded on the back, apices acute</td>
